node.title: Inside the Gilgo Beach murders investigation
node.description: A suspect has been taken into custody on New York's Long Island in connection with a long-unsolved string of killings known as the Gilgo Beach murders. "48 Hours" goes inside the search for a serial killer.
node.content: ["A suspect has been taken into custody on New York's Long Island in connection with a long-unsolved string of killings known as the Gilgo Beach murders. Law enforcement sources have identified him as Rex Heuermann, an architect who lives across the bay from where some of the bodies were found."]
